            <title>1.5.2</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 17:04:52 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>15</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.5.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed status bar context window display fluctuating between 123K and 155K due to the API dynamically changing `maxOutputTokens`. Now uses a fixed 8K buffer matching the CC extension's own calculation, showing a stable 192K for 200K context models.
]]></description>
