            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Bug Fixes

- Fix extension updater downloading wrong platform VSIX — added `?targetPlatform=` parameter to VS Code Marketplace download URLs. Without this, the marketplace returned a universal/Windows package instead of the macOS ARM64 one, causing the bundled CLI binary to be unusable (#20)
]]></description>
